@node install "Installation"

 Use the provided installer-script or just copy the AvailMem executable
 with icon to your WBStartup-drawer.

@endnode

@node source "Source Codes"

 What? Is the complete source-codes for availmem included in the archive?

 Of course it is. Over 2000 lines of pure assembly code with at least a
 2-3 words comment after every instruction. (Except the GUI, as it's
 generated.) A complete dream for the 'misguided' programmer and a good
 reference for the experienced coder.

 @{"Show it to me!!!" link showsource}

@endnode

