@node register "Registering"

 What? You want me to PAY for this crap? :)

 Of course not. If you send me an email I will assemble a personal copy of
 AvailMem with your name in the About requester. Ok, anyone who can read
 the source-code can change the text, but I want to check how widespread
 the use of this program is. And as a bonus, you will receive every update
 of AvailMem.

 And please, an email is all I ask for.

@endnode

